divs: Sighting DetailsDriving home after picking up my sister from UCSD. Going south of the 15 freeway. about 5-10 minutes getting on that freeway noticed a White glow object the glow was not wavering. Observed the object until we got home. While observing the object noticed 2-4 planes observing the object as well. It was amazing. Lost sight of the object because of the tree line near our place.
trends: There have been no other sightings in San Diego to Rancho Cucam
